Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) are considered an important technology in terms of high efficiency and clean energy generation.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: Flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC) which is a combination of tubular and planar cell geometries stands out with its performance values and low costs.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: In this study, the performance of an FT-SOFC is analyzed numerically by using finite element method-based design as a result of changing parameters by using different fuels which are pure hydrogen and coal gas with various proportions of CO.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: In addition, cell performance values for different temperatures were analyzed and interpreted.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: Analyzes have been performed by using COMSOL Multiphysics software.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: The rates of CO composition used are 10%, 20%, and 40%, respectively.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: In addition, the air was used as the oxidizer in all cases.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: The cell voltage and average cell power of the FT-SOFC were examined under the 800 degrees C operating condition.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: The maximum power value and current density value were obtained as 710 W/m(2) and 1420 A/m(2) for the flat-tubular cell, respectively.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: As a result of the study, it was observed that the maximum cell power densities increased with increasing temperature.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: Analysis results showed that FT-SOFCs have suitable properties for different fuel usage and different operating temperatures.
Titulo: Simulation of hydrogen and coal gas fueled flat-tubular solid oxide fuel cell (FT-SOFC)

Sentencas: High-performance values and design features in different operating conditions are expected to make FT-SOFC the focus of many studies in the future.
